JSX whitespace model: cosmetic indentation between block children is collapsed by
wsnorm before emit, so the generated code emits NO whitespace-only gw.S calls
between the elements. A regression that unwires wsnorm would re-introduce
gw.S("\n\t\t") calls here. Fragment root avoids the fallthrough Attrs machinery.
-- input.gsx --
package views

component Layout() {
	<>
		<header>Top</header>
		<main>Body</main>
		<footer>End</footer>
	</>
}
-- invoke --
Layout()
-- diagnostics.golden --
-- render.golden --
<header>Top</header><main>Body</main><footer>End</footer>
